commentsData.body:
A mode where you can set the time to fall asleep and the time to wake up and legit fall asleep and wake up right at those times and then be ready for the day.

&#x200B;

I toss and turn so much at night.

No need for a blanket or a bed, just be comfortable wherever you are, like a dog that does three circles and just plops down on a bare hardwood floor in the middle of winter and just snoozes away without a care in the world. Also just for the sake of saving nightmares, you can't be attacked while in this state, because killing someone in their sleep is pretty shitty (seriously fuck you liveleak and brazil for the nightmares).

&#x200B;

Also, sleeping completely heals pain and sickness the next day like in video-games, specifically like visiting a hospital in Earthbound, where you just walk in, pay 30 bucks and your entire gang is revived even though they just got mowed down by some random ass hippy or a rabid mushroom or something.

&#x200B;

Also, this is more hotel related, but I want the ability to call my dad and save my game so if I fuck up and talk shit to the wrong person or whatever and get killed I can just spawn back at the hotel where the phone is and just continue like nothing ever happened...
